{
  "stem": "18770.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 21.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My mother actually reconnects with my governess.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Find-- I mean, she must receive a letter from her and begins to send her packages-- food.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Now she's living in Poland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "To me, this governess, who was my mother more than my mother, I must-- without being aware of it at the time-- must have been really angry about her leaving.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You know, a child doesn't understand why somebody like that leaves you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because I never write to her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I could have easily added something to a letter my mother was writing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I'm sure my mother even probably said to me, why don't you write?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "No, I never write to her, never want to know much about her.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it's only years later when I go to my mother's house-- many years later-- and there is a photograph lying out on the table by the phone in her house.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I look at that picture.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember what my governess looks like.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I pick up the picture and without hardly knowing--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Her name is [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Stepha. ?] And with hardly knowing what I'm doing, I take the picture, and I kiss it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By the time I'm in my 20s or 30s.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So you can see how deep that thing was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But my mother reconnects with her and continues to send her things until, I guess, eventually she dies, probably of old age or whatever.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What do I do?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I go to-- I go to-- I finish with PS 87.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I go-- so we're living in Manhattan on the West Side.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We moved to 81st Street.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I go to the Bronx High School of Science-- genius school, 98% Jewish, one token black, one token Oriental kid.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And an amazing school.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, I only bother to-- usually you don't mention high school.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
